<sect1 id="Filter.Unconnected">
	<title>Unconnected</title>
	<para>
		The Unconnected Filter allows users to change the visibility of
		unconnected concepts (i.e. no relations existing whether visible or
		invisible).
	</para>
	<para>
		<screenshot>
			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata align="center"
						fileref="../images/filter/filter_unconnected1.png" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</screenshot>
	</para>
	<para>
		After applying the Unconnected Filter:
	</para>
	<para>
		<screenshot>
			<mediaobject>
